The Team Antonios Papavasileiou The man with the plan. He wanted to create an AI by doing if else statements so deep you\'d probably find diamonds. Instead he spent half his week doing SQL inserts for this app. The design and the team have no one else to thank but him. Alket Saliaj Quite the mystery this man. He speak little, codes a lot. He creates Java but surprisingly, doesn\'t drink it. He prefers Gin and Juice like a true gentleman. Elias Kodoulas A visionary. Dude writes java almost as good as the one he drinks. Developing is to him like photosynthesizing is to plants. Friends constantly tell him \"Den ise edo\" because honestly, he never is there to play with them, he\'s either androiding or making bolognese.
